(4) To tune the hard drive :

Reboot may required.

nano /etc/rc.local

Add the following above "exit 0" -

echo 1024 > /sys/block/sda/queue/read_ahead_kb
echo 256 > /sys/block/sda/queue/nr_requests

(5) To tune the file system :

Reboot may required.

nano /etc/fstab

add "discard,nodiratime,noatime" just before "errors=remount-ro" and "defaults"
